		b Division
	p $$a/b=c$$
	p Note that:
	p $$c=\frac{a_1-a_2}{b_1-b_2}$$
	p $$c=\frac{(a_1-a_2)(b_1-b_2)}{(b_1-b_2)(b_1-b_2)}$$
	p $$c=\frac{(a_1b_1+a_2b_2)-(a_2b_1+a_1b_2) }{b_1b_1+b_2b_2-2b_1b_2}$$
	p So:
